{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM05_ST4_670.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x29,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Sis, Sis... Wake up, Sis...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hrmm, five more minutes...<CR>Nooo, actually ten more minutes..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Goodness, you're still so bad at waking up in the morning... Please wake uuup!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Huh...? Nio!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x138,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Wah! Don't wake up so suddenly!<CR>You scared me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Oh, sorry. I've been waiting for you to visit me for so long."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I'm so glad. I thought that maybe I wouldn't be able to see you again."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x13a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "So, it's been that long? I've been asleep the whole time, so I couldn't tell."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Even when I woke up every now and then, it was all dark and I couldn't find a way out..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I couldn't tell where you were."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "It was as if I was locked up somewhere."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "But, I'm glad I was able to see you again, Sis."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Hehe, me too. I'm happy I got to see your face..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1a2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Oh, that's right! I made this for you, Nio. See, isn't it cute?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "So, even if we're far apart, we'll still feel like we're close."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "You...made this?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Yup! I worked real hard on it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Yay! Thank you, Sis!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x45,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Hmhmhm, it's cute! I wonder what I should name it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "You look so cute when you're holding a stuffed animal!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Your idea of cute isn't always dependable..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "You say everything I wear and have is cute."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "That's...cuz it really is all cute.<CR>I'm not lying to you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Hehe, but this stuffed animal is cute. Thank you, Sis."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I feel like you're gonna be close to me from now on."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I'll take good care of it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Hey, wake up. How long do you plan on coveting this slumber?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hrmm, Nio's so cute...<CR>She's just like a fairy...<CR>Zzz zzz..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "You can't hide behind that stupid<CR>sleeping face of yours forever.<CR>I'm telling you to wake up!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "*yawn* ...Oh, Mr. Keith. Good morning."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "That's right. I was giving Nio the stuffed animal..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "From the looks of it, it seems you succeeded in giving it to her."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Where is it now?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "The needle is pointing...northeast of here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x91,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "I recall that area as having nothing... I guess that was all a deception."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "First, I think I'll head over there. Maybe I'll get to see Nio!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x93,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "Good. With how things are going, the sooner you act, the better. However..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "He doesn't seem to care about hurting humans."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "With all you've been through,<CR>I'm sure you won't go down easily,<CR>but make sure you're fully prepared."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "If necessary, I'll go along with you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "Thank you so much. I'll go get prepared right away!"
        }
    ]
}